WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.280
Now we're getting somewhere.

2
00:00:02.280 --> 00:00:04.920
It was her FriendlyBook account
 that posted on social

3
00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:07.560
